## Instructions

Use your browser tools to research this topic. Here's a recommended workflow:

1. navigate(url: "https://www.google.com") - Start at Google
2. fill_form(field: "q", value: "<%= @topic %>") - Enter the search query
3. click(text: "Google Search") - Submit the search
4. extract_links() - Get the search result URLs
5. navigate(url: "...") - Visit promising results
6. extract_main_content() - Read the page content
7. Repeat steps 5-6 for multiple sources

Remember: fill_form requires both "field" and "value" parameters.

